item.title: How to make a server with hamachi? (think i kno)
item.dc:creator: @_ownage1 ~ownage~
item.description:
@_ownage1 wrote:

It’s easy, first you download hamachi, you turn it on and see the i.p. at the top, you use that as your i.p. Now to make networks, you make networks download a source (fr33sc4p3 my favorite) extract it to your desktop using .rar, open compile choose r log on put in i.p. (43594) and your i.p., you just made a server.
